{"tid":348126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘綫列車受阻逾9小時　港鐵仍未完成修復","createTime":"2017-08-05T12:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T12:59:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"362a827211cda78613f85fbc55f7f34925a23cdf","tid":348126,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"5d5778daff2898774b98dd822d080c55b03c551b","tid":348126,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"windows 有 bug ，受害人中勒索軟件，遺失重要資料<br />\nmicrosoft 一蚊都唔洗賠"},{"pid":"95bfb62eea9067b76e1f78e19b7465ff1f0e334a","tid":348126,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵9日內發生第5宗故障，令列車服務受阻，今次出事的是觀塘綫觀塘站，信號故障由早上11時14分開始，逾9小時仍未修復。根據票價調整機制，港鐵今次事故或至少要被罰2,000萬元，金額於下年度用來提供即日第二程回贈優惠。<br />\n<br />\n受今次故障影響，觀塘綫列車要慢駛，額外行車時間一度增至15分鐘，約每8分鐘才有一班列車。港鐵一度要提供免費接駁巴士服務，疏導乘客。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行票價調整機制，港鐵每宗事故的罰款額，是依列車服務受阻的時間而遞增，受阻逾31分鐘，至少罰100萬元；受阻逾3小時，至少罰500萬元；受阻逾4小時後的每個小時（或不足1小時），再罰多250萬元，每宗事故最多罰2,500萬元。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人回應指，今次事故原因仍在調查，若證實事故是因港鐵在營運過程的機件故障或人為因素，而導致長時間服務延誤或暫停，便會按機制繳交罰款。"},{"pid":"c82111b451f55f94cb48879159f4f3288b5ab804","tid":348126,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57044702&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57044702%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170805&d=0BBrEFywiakRo5xT09%2Fk3JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=8d3f9253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57044702%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170805&h=b5ba3bc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57044702&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170805</a>"},{"pid":"19797f341b92ffa3f36e349c9442aab0557834b6","tid":348126,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}